{"tid":2388461,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖)終於搵到插件取代chrome個google translate,咁轉用firefox啦屌","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T14:09:31.000Z","uid":249378,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"abc83d3b9785b616d4f157b6d304992bc2891250","tid":2388461,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"死罪1:依家chrome開機service由一個加到三個 service<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iHQnPr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iHQnPr.png&h=2e0743c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死罪2:長期RAM佔用率高(50%倒)<br />\n死罪3:更新完成日crush(如果D野冇autosave收得皮,建議養成ctrl + s好習慣)<br />\n死罪4:十年如一日嘅google theme<br />\n死罪5:更新完書籤要按多下select<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死罪6:d chrome實驗成鳩日改名搵唔返改個d settings<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係chrome原生插件google translate搵唔到取代一早轉鳩咗,firefox addOn不嬲多人玩d<br />\n取代品:<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">Simple Translate</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYxEgrz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYxEgrz.png&h=50331f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ES3W26z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FES3W26z.png&h=67f634b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/addon/simple-translate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fzh-TW%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fsimple-translate%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=0804a4e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/addon/simple-translate/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">youtube子母畫面</span></span><br />\n仲有個firefox 71 ver.更新到youtube可以子母畫面separate成個別視窗,個視窗仲係可以draggable同resizable,屌打原生youtube迷你播放器同Enhancer for Youtube&trade; fi