/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsFOajg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsFOajg.png&h=3b1d3b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/lockwise/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Flockwise%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=b5b387c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/lockwise/</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗要適應layout之外其他基本野唔使講,d browser快捷鍵同chrome一樣,插件種類多過chrome <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">快d一齊換啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"我就信唔過firefox lockwise<br />\n另外如果堅持要用firefox我唔建議login<br />\nbookmarks可以經xml檔import<br />\npasswords就用password manager (e.g. bitwarden)<br />\n如果係首次用password manager，可以將原本用緊既browser既儲存password既csv檔export出黎再import入去manager"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"import完去manager後記得刪返電腦上既csv檔，因為個檔係完全無加密既text file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7569ab15bfd02678814bd01f3a4d98307a715d","tid":2388461,"uid":330227,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d89ffd3fe5db49b4220c3c4ed1a626a222eddd53","tid":2388461,"uid":5056,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e944e2f5d44699aa8dfc53151eaa18b6504bba3a","tid":2388461,"uid":249378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f2fc410809ef919940428913882442dac8cc112","tid":2388461,"uid":5056,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"可唔可以叫返extension<br />\n插件好難聽<br />\n插你個件"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"chill 不如我上reddit打大段英文,你再comment我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔想打英文，你可以用返chrome 自己個譯法：「擴