%2Fi%2FES3W26z.png&h=67f634b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/addon/simple-translate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fzh-TW%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fsimple-translate%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=0804a4e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/addon/simple-translate/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">youtube子母畫面</span></span><br />\n仲有個firefox 71 ver.更新到youtube可以子母畫面separate成個別視窗,個視窗仲係可以draggable同resizable,屌打原生youtube迷你播放器同Enhancer for Youtube&trade; fix死係一個頁面入面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDi4stK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDi4stK.png&h=031dca1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://support.mozilla.org/zh-TW/kb/about-picture-picture-firefox\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.mozilla.org%2Fzh-TW%2Fkb%2Fabout-picture-picture-firefox&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=32256ee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.mozilla.org/zh-TW/kb/about-picture-picture-firefox</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">Firefox會定期推薦theme</span></span><br />\nTheme可以保留新鮮感,你極簡開都會審美疲勞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uznY3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uznY3b.png&h=4d4fbfdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔like又可以自己custome theme,friendly到唔洗自學css<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk9rGgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk9rGgO.png&h=b31e3b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">Firefox Lockwise</span></span><br />\nFirefox自家password同步儲存軟件,帶android同ios,最緊要係咩?獨立於firefox自成軟件又可以sync翻firefox browser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsFOajg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsFOajg.png&h=3b1d3b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/lockwise/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Flockwise%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=b5b387c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/lockwise/</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗要適應layout之外其他基本野唔使講,d browser快捷鍵同chrome一樣,插件種類多過chrome <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">快d一齊換啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"我就信唔過firefox lockwise<br />\n另外如果堅持要用firefox我唔建議login<br />\nbookmarks可以經xml檔import<br />\npasswords就用password manager (e.g. bitwarden)<br />\n如果係首次用password manager，可以將原本用緊既browser既儲存password既csv檔export出黎再import入去manager"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"啱啊 Firefox連自己個 browser嘅 security都搞唔掂<br />\n為人垢病 仲信佢個所謂 password manager?"}]}